Mary, Sara and Brent:

Mark H. has asked me to join Elizabeth's group which I have agreed to do

while I continue to support Julia's group on the physical trading side.  I

plan to meet with Mark T. later this week to go over what files I will keep

and what files I will not keep.  My tentative plan is to finish all of the

day to day stuff and to hand over most of the special projects/ longer term

stuff.  With that in mind, please give some thought about who should handle

the hedge fund work, Canada back-up, the KCS VPP, coordinating our offsite

and the remaining legal/credit conferences, negotiating the Japan ISDA's (I

have created the forms and drafts of Schedules have been sent out), point

person for EIM financial trading issues, and credit derivatives back-up and

let me know what you think.


